---
title: Salsa Verde Sole with Roasted Potatoes and Green Beans
description: Every cuisine has its own version of a green sauce. In Argentina, it’s chimichurri; in France, it’s sauce verte; and in Spain and Italy, salsa verde. Our chefs put their own spin on the Italian version by incorporating green olives and parsley. They add a major pop of flavor to this light and breezy but completely satisfying dinner.
